Usage:
  lark-cli base +field-list [flags]

Flags:
      --as string           identity type: user | bot
      --base-token string   base token
      --dry-run             print request without executing
  -h, --help                help for +field-list
  -q, --jq string           jq expression to filter JSON output
      --limit int           pagination size (default 100)
      --offset int          pagination offset
      --table-id string     table ID (must start with tbl if ID) or name

